# demo.nlt — sample nlpilot script for the IDE
@web
Go to https://duckduckgo.com
Type "nlpilot" into the search field and press enter
Wait 2 seconds
EXPECT that the page contains the text "nlpilot"
SAVE a screenshot of the page to "results.png"

@bash
Print the current working directory
EXPECT the output contains "${project}"

